11:["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-5 text-base leading-8 text-slate-200","children":[["$","p","If your Amazon seller account has been suspended, you are likely losing revenue every single day. For many sellers, that can mean thousands of dollars in missed sales, delayed cash flow, and mounting operational pressure.",{"children":"If your Amazon seller account has been suspended, you are likely losing revenue every single day. For many sellers, that can mean thousands of dollars in missed sales, delayed cash flow, and mounting operational pressure."}],["$","p","The good news is that most suspensions can be reversed if they are handled correctly. The key is speed, accuracy, and a strategy that addresses what Amazon is really asking for.",{"children":"The good news is that most suspensions can be reversed if they are handled correctly. The key is speed, accuracy, and a strategy that addresses what Amazon is really asking for."}]]}]
